#

Lemon Herb Grilled Salmon with Asparagus

$18.99
500 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

HealthySeafoodGrilledSummer

Description

A light and flavorful salmon dish, perfectly grilled with a zesty lemon herb marinade, served alongside crisp asparagus.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz each)
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Fresh lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic clove, minced: 1
  • Fresh dill, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • Asparagus spears: 1 bunch
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
